




1- we should create a "deployment.yaml" file instead of 

"kubectl create deployment first-app --image=hamidhszd/kub-first-app"  command:










deployment.yaml:


apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: second-app-deployment
spec:
  replicas: 1
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: second-app
      tier: backend
  template:
    metadata: 
      labels:
        app: second-app
        tier: backend
    spec: 
      containers:
        - name: second-node
          image: hamidhszd/kub-second-app
        # - name: ...
        #   image: ...












------------------------------------------------



name: second-app-deployment



replicas: 1



image: hamidhszd/kub-second-app



------------------------------------------------



2-


â–¶ kubectl apply -f=deployment.yaml

deployment.apps/second-app-deployment created





------------------------------------------------
------------------------------------------------
------------------------------------------------
------------------------------------------------
------------------------------------------------
------------------------------------------------



Create service:




3- we should create a "service.yaml" file instead of 

"kubectl expose deployment first-app --type=LoadBalancer --port=8080"  command:








service.yaml:



apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: backend
spec:
  selector: 
    app: second-app
  ports:
    - protocol: 'TCP'
      port: 80
      targetPort: 8080
    # - protocol: 'TCP'
    #   port: 443
    #   targetPort: 443
  type: LoadBalancer





------------------------------------------------


name: backend




  selector: 
    app: second-app



port: 80                  --->   the port that we want to expose

targetPort: 8080          --->   the port inside the container

type: LoadBalancer


------------------------------------------------



4-


â–¶ kubectl apply -f=service.yaml   

service/backend created




------------------------------------------------
------------------------------------------------
------------------------------------------------
------------------------------------------------
